buyGood(bytes32,bytes32,uint128,uint256,.notice: sell _swapQuantity units of good1 to buy good2~用户出售_swapQuantity个_goodid1去购买 _goodid2

check_banlist(address).notice: Returns the address's status 查询地址是否被禁止提手续费

goodNum().notice: Returns the good's total number of the market 返回市场商品总数

removebanlist(address).notice: rm ban list  移除禁止名单
